Thanks so much for
joining us today Melissa.

00:05:29.090 --> 00:05:30.210
It's been great having you.

00:05:30.210 --> 00:05:30.800
MELISSA KONDRICK:
It's been a blast.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:31.674
Thanks for having me.

